lass=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n返返正題<br />\n家境貧困 所以未正式出身都返過唔少工<br />\n勞動嘅開心一定係跟車 同個c fu追時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />hehehaha又一工<br />\n坐嘅返pr pt 見識到賣腦嘅人嘅世界 <br />\n可能因為個時年紀唔大又或者好好彩 個陣啲人都好錫我 好遇肯袋錢入我袋 啲是非又鐘意同我講 可惜冇份工可以長做 次次總係有啲嘢搞到冇得返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過做得越多工就越發現世界真係好唔公平 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08522a268db5aa6c9c9bcd946135eaae4545752d","tid":1829072,"uid":216643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c37ac03ef86b3ed0d79fe791e6497f247b2e2c7a","tid":1829072,"uid":156908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a9ed1d9d15a6ba3198ad1775c09df87daa4c3a5","tid":1829072,"uid":216643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ba58d0ce4f631825e33406620861152dcca4003","tid":1829072,"uid":73163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T21:22:51.000Z","msg":"corporate sales 係做咩的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T01:37:54.000Z","msg":"Business to business"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T18:15:09.000Z","msg":"想問做b2b sales大唔大壓力 好唔好做？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T00:53:34.000Z","msg":"大壓力到爆，之前都做過retail ,但b2b 完全唔同。<br />\n捱得過開頭嗰段（半年到），之後就好好搵嘅。如果有好嘅account"},{"pid":"347b317639b0659bb930ae795afac836f20f2432","tid":1829072,"uid":48452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T01:02:11.000Z","msg":"最鍾意私補 幫到人又有滿足感<br />\n其次係水電佬 我鍾意手藝嘢<br />\n但兩份都因為一啲原因被迫放棄咗<br />\n而家做我最憎嘅工種"},{"pid":"3de5dbaa4f0bc94227c995b95421c05071419a70","tid":1829072,"uid":90702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T01:05:30.000Z","msg":"返倉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />見識到原來一件貨係點樣由個倉再送到你手上<br />\n倉務物流原來係咁<br />\n雖然倉份工會俾啲朋友厭棄唔返 但我覺得返得唔錯<br />\n全日做毒撚唔駛同人講野自摺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\